<p>To create a new link (i.e., an Internet Shortcut) just do this in the main form:</p>

<ol>
<li>Type a name;
<li>Type a valid URL begining with one scheme of "http://" or "https://" followed  by a canonical full qualified name.
<li>Click on the "Save Link" button.
</ol>

<note>
The new link will be saved with "name.url" filename in your Home Favorites Folder. 
</note>
